  "general_provisions": "This bill amends provisions related to local referendums. ",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>defines terms;<hr><ltbullet>subject to certain exceptions, establishes a process for voters who are residents of a school district to hold a local referendum on any legislative action taken by the local school board, including the local school board's decision to increase a tax or impose a new tax; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes.",
